  esc1.writeMicroseconds(1200);
  esc2.writeMicroseconds(1200);
  esc3.writeMicroseconds(1200);
  esc4.writeMicroseconds(1200);
}
```

**Summary of fixes:**
1. Added 1000–2000 range to attach()
2. Replaced write() with writeMicroseconds()
3. Added arming sequence before any throttle

