**Three bugs causing violent oscillation:**

**Bug 1 — Integral not scaled by dt:**
`integral += error` accumulates raw error values regardless of time step. This makes integral windup proportional to loop rate, not time. At 250Hz, integral grows 250x faster than at 1Hz.

**Fix:**
```c
