┌────┬─────┬─────┬──────┬─────┬─────┬─────┬─────┐
│ –  │EEPM1│EEPM0│ EERIE│EEMPE│ EEPE│ EERE│     │
└────┴─────┴─────┴──────┴─────┴─────┴─────┴─────┘
  7     6     5     4     3     2     1    0

- EERE  = EEPROM Read Enable (write 1 to start read)
- EEPE  = EEPROM Program Enable (write 1 to start write)
- EEMPE = EEPROM Master Program Enable (must write 1 within 4 cycles before EEPE)
- EERIE = EEPROM Ready Interrupt Enable
- EEPM1:EEPM0 = Programming mode:
  00 = Erase+Write (3.4ms)
  01 = Erase only (1.8ms)
  10 = Write only (1.8ms)

ATmega328P EEPROM Specs:
- Size: 1024 bytes (addresses 0x000–0x3FF)
- Write endurance: 100,000 cycles
- Retention: > 20 years at 25°C
- Write time: ~3.4ms per byte

