┌─────┬─────┬──────┬──────┬──────┬───────┬───────┬───────┐
│EXCLK│ AS2 │TCN2UB│OCR2AUB│OCR2BUB│TCR2AUB│TCR2BUB│     │
└─────┴─────┴──────┴──────┴──────┴───────┴───────┴───────┘

- AS2=1 → Asynchronous mode (external crystal)
- TCN2UB: Timer counter update busy flag
- TCR2AUB/TCR2BUB: Control register update busy
- MUST wait for these to clear before accessing Timer2 registers!

Timer2 Prescaler options with 32.768 kHz:
/1   → 128 Hz overflow
/8   → 16 Hz overflow
/32  → 4 Hz overflow
/64  → 2 Hz overflow
/128 → 1 Hz overflow ← perfect for RTC
/256 → 0.5 Hz overflow
/1024→ 0.125 Hz overflow

