TCCR1B Input Capture Bits:
- ICES1: Input Capture Edge Select
  0 = Falling edge triggers capture
  1 = Rising edge triggers capture
- ICNC1: Input Capture Noise Canceler
  1 = 4 consecutive equal samples required (delays by 4 clocks)

ICU Measurement Process:
1. Detect rising edge → save timer value → reset timer → switch to falling edge
2. Detect falling edge → save timer value = pulse width
3. Convert ticks to time: time_µs = ticks / (F_CPU / prescaler / 1,000,000)

At /8 prescaler: 1 tick = 0.5µs → divide by 2 for µs
At /1 prescaler: 1 tick = 0.0625µs → divide by 16 for µs (better resolution)

