- `WL_IDLE_STATUS (0)` — WiFi idle
- `WL_NO_SSID_AVAIL (1)` — SSID not found
- `WL_CONNECTED (3)` — connected
- `WL_CONNECT_FAILED (4)` — wrong password
- `WL_DISCONNECTED (6)` — disconnected

